title: First Visits to Revisting The Breakfast Club
itunes:title: First Visits to Revisting The Breakfast Club
description:
Thurs 12/29- As 2017 approaches, the Breakfast Club is giving their best interviews of 2016. Today featured two guest that never been on the show which is Future and Regina Hall, followed by Kevin Liles and Diddy. Charlamagne also rewarded Jason Stokes and Samantha Martinez for Donkey of the Day.
